WEBVTT

00:05:59.120 --> 00:06:01.949
Now the priest’s spell failed.

00:06:01.973 --> 00:06:06.136
So being an honorable man,
he got back to his hymns and verses

00:06:06.160 --> 00:06:07.896
and then started meditating.

00:06:07.920 --> 00:06:11.376
Fierce meditation.
Intense meditation.

00:06:11.400 --> 00:06:13.640
This time, God himself descended.

00:06:15.120 --> 00:06:17.816
He said, "Ask whatever you want."

00:06:17.840 --> 00:06:21.296
The priest folded his hands,
fell at the God’s feet and prayed:

00:06:21.320 --> 00:06:26.696
"God, please grant me courage,
intelligence, cleverness and a vocabulary

00:06:26.720 --> 00:06:29.736
so I can match
up to the priestess’s smartness."

00:06:29.760 --> 00:06:32.896
As he asked for this, God
changed his demeanor and said,